  <ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🚨 <strong>Staple line leak</strong> (medical emergency requiring hospitalization)</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🚨 <strong>Severe nausea and vomiting</strong> (dehydration, malnutrition)</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🚨 <strong>Stomach distension</strong> (stretching your new stomach permanently)</li>
