  <li>Portion: 1/2 - 1 cup per meal</li>
  <li>Never skip meals</li>
</ul>

<h4>3. Chew Thoroughly</h4>

<ul>
  <li>20-30 chews per bite</li>
  <li>Put utensils down between bites</li>
  <li>Eat slowly (20-30 minutes minimum)</li>
</ul>

<h4>4. Hydrate Between Meals</h4>

<ul>
  <li>2L+ daily</li>
  <li>No drinking 30 min before/after meals</li>
  <li>Sip throughout day</li>
</ul>

<h4>5. Avoid Grazing</h4>

<ul>
